            "heading": "Before the round",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>You’ve set up your sensors and Arccos account. Next, open the app, choose your course and tracking device, then start your round.</p><p>Not playing yet? You can use Arccos to preview the course and plan your strategies.</p>",
